# AI Antiseptic User Manual
**Version 0.1.0** • Fully private • Grounded RAG system

## What is AI Antiseptic?
A 100 % open-source, NotebookLM-style tool that forces every answer to come from **your documents only**.  
No hallucinations • Full citations • Works offline • Optional podcast-style audio overviews.

## Quick Start (30 seconds)
1. Put any PDFs, .txt, or .md files into the `sources/` folder  
2. Run:
   ```bash
   python run.py "Your question here"

   Supported File Types

PDF (.pdf)
Plain text (.txt)
Markdown (.md, .markdown)

